rows.label: tlk47100041_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm a bit of an oddball compared to
most Phonex.

rows.label: tlk47100041_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You don't normally see us fitting in
with humans.

rows.label: tlk47100041_01_msg0003
rows.name:
In fact, I don't think you'll find anyone
besides me here in Fons Maim.

rows.label: tlk47100041_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I don't really see what's so great about
having to forage for food and eat yucky
plants all the time.

rows.label: tlk47100041_01_msg0005
rows.name:
No, I'd much prefer lapping up the
life of luxury here!

rows.label: tlk47100041_01_msg0006
rows.name:
There are lots of big brawny Invidians
that take good care of me. They feed
every day without fail.
